{"tid":1284038,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉兆佳：特赦或鼓勵年輕人墮法網","createTime":"2019-07-04T04:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T04:11:15.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9b69501f2b28546ea6b4042b701b3217134d23b6","tid":1284038,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190704/s00001/4d0acf8af3cad56cb183d64338b9a1c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190704%2Fs00001%2F4d0acf8af3cad56cb183d64338b9a1c3.jpg&h=9d13b554&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n修訂《逃犯條例》爭議未息，觸發連場示威衝突，當中有建議稱，重啟政改可紓解紛爭。<br />\n<br />\n全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳出席新城電台節目時稱，經歷一連串事件後，中央以更強硬姿態對待政改，現時重啟政改只會令港府陷入更深政治爭拗，未必能解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n至於有建議認為特首可特赦被捕示威者，劉兆佳認為不可能，因社會仍贊成嚴肅處理暴力事件，特赦未能符合社會期望；他又擔心，如果對這類情況沒有懲罰，會鼓勵更多年輕人墮入法網。<br />\n<br />\n他又認為，現時修例爭議不但有內部暴力事件，更牽涉至外交層面，且帶動社會存在的結構性深層次矛盾也一次過爆發出來，相信短期內修例爭議「無得收科」。"},{"pid":"68ec782e40cf0c6a78456b9716958f832813af93","tid":1284038,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:07:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190704/s00001/1562208930326/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190704%2Fs00001%2F1562208930326%2F&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFIw2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=1de35f56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190704%2Fs00001%2F1562208930326%2F&h=122f031f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190704/s00001/1562208930326/</a>"},{"pid":"a03e823ad127d66e916df9585a2d8a28c568c283","tid":1284038,"uid":255105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:08:54.000Z","msg":"反對特赦或鼓勵政權繼續漠視民意"},{"pid":"9b1f293386a728b3a2e1b8c1141fa844b759fdec","tid":1284038,"uid":22231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201